text: Syeda Wahida Sabrina is a Bangladeshi film actress. She won the Bangladesh National Film Award for Best Child Artist twice, for the films Gangajatra (2009) and Antardhan (2012). ==Selected films== * Gangajatra - 2009 * Antardhan - 2012 * Shesh Kotha - 2017 ==Awards and nominations== National Film Awards {| border="1" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;" |- style="background:#ccc; text-align:center;" !
